#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Knight katana"
msgid_plural "Knight katanas"
msgstr[0] "騎士刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Knight katana'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"This is a sword that Japanese ninja deal with. It is a straight sword with "
"no warpage, with a length intermediate between the sword and chisel. I could"
" also use it to climb the wall with my legs on the brim."
msgstr "這是日本忍者使用的刀。這是一把無彎曲的直刀，長度介於刀與鑿之間。我還可以用它踩著刀緣攀爬牆壁。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Kusari gama"
msgid_plural "Kusari gamas"
msgstr[0] "鎖鐮"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Kusari gama'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"It is a weapon that connects weights to a mowing scythe with a long chain. "
"It was mainly used as a hidden weapon. By throwing the weight like a sling, "
"you can hit an enemy of a distant intervalã€"
msgstr "這是一種用長鏈將重物連接到鐮刀上的武器。它主要被用作暗器。通過像投石索一樣投擲重物，可以擊中遠距離的敵人。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Nunchuku"
msgid_plural "Nunchukus"
msgstr[0] "雙節棍"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Nunchuku'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"It is a weapon originating from Okinawa in Japan. By interwoven fighting by "
"bare hands, we can shoot a variety of blows while dazzling our opponent. You"
" wish you were Bruce Lee."
msgstr "這是一種源自日本沖繩的武器。通過徒手交織搏擊，我們可以在迷惑對手的同時施展多種打擊。你希望自己是李小龍。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Scroll of thunder release art"
msgid_plural "Scroll of thunder release art"
msgstr[0] "雷遁術卷軸"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"It is a discharge device which camouflaged as a scroll ... where the "
"technique of thunder release was written. It operates by feeding power from "
"the UPS. Furess is a technique to escape. Get away from the zombie while he "
"is immobilized."
msgstr "這是一種偽裝成卷軸的放電裝置……上面記載了雷遁之術。它通過從UPS供電來運作。風雷遁是一種逃脫技巧。在殭屍無法動彈時趁機遠離。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json .\ninja_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\ninja_toos.json .\ninja_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自動"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Scroll of fire art"
msgid_plural "Scrolls of fire art"
msgstr[0] "火遁卷軸"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"It is an outright flamethrower that disguised as a scroll ... where art of "
"fire abstinence was written. Fill with gasoline or napalm and use. Furess is"
" a technique to escape. Let's get away with the zombies burning."
msgstr "這是一種偽裝成卷軸的直噴式火焰噴射器……上面記載了火遁禁術。填充汽油或凝固汽油後使用。風雷遁是一種逃脫技巧。讓我們在殭屍燃燒時趁機脫身。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Scroll of afterimage"
msgid_plural "Scroll of afterimages"
msgstr[0] "殘影卷軸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Scroll of afterimage'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"It is a portable fog screen disguised as scroll of divisional technique. "
"Collect the moisture in the air and scatter it as fog and project the "
"afterimage with the projector. The effect time is very short and the image "
"seems rather blurred, but in a moment it may be possible to make the enemy "
"dazzle."
msgstr ""
"這是一種偽裝成分身術卷軸的便攜式霧屏。收集空氣中的水分並將其散佈為霧氣，並通過投影儀投射殘影。效果時間很短，圖像看起來相當模糊，但瞬間或許能讓敵人眼花繚亂。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Tornado technique scroll"
msgid_plural "Tornado technique scrolls"
msgstr[0] "龍捲風術卷軸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tornado technique scroll'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"It is a new type of vacuum cleaner that disguised as a scroll of tornado's "
"technique. * We clean the surroundings by raising a tornado. Its attractive "
"force does not decay, it is difficult to control, so you need to be careful "
"when you use it."
msgstr "這是一種偽裝成龍捲風術卷軸的新型吸塵器。*我們通過掀起龍捲風來清理周圍環境。其吸引力不會衰減，但難以控制，因此使用時需小心。"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'Decoy doll'}.
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "The decoy doll seems to be dancing."
msgstr "誘餌人偶似乎在跳舞。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'Decoy doll'}.
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid " set up a decoy doll, but the control string has run out."
msgstr "設置了誘餌人偶，但控制線已用完。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Decoy doll'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"I put on shirts on trees and attached strings so that I could produce "
"movement. If you have bad heads, you will mistake this doll for you and show"
" off your ski. It installs it by using it."
msgstr "我在樹上套上襯衫並繫上線，以便能產生動作。如果敵人頭腦不好，就會誤以為這個人偶是你，並炫耀其滑雪技巧。通過使用它來安裝。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Black armor"
msgid_plural "Black armors"
msgstr[0] "黑色護甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Black armor'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"These are ninja clothes. It is black in order to be able to blend in with "
"the dark night. In reality, the actual ninja wore leaf colored camoflage."
msgstr "這是忍者服裝。為了能與黑夜融為一體，它被設計成黑色。實際上，真正的忍者穿的是葉色迷彩服。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Survivor ninja suit"
msgid_plural "Survivor ninja suits"
msgstr[0] "倖存者忍者服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Survivor ninja suit'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"We reinforced the black sheath with modern materials. From the ancient "
"times, the main character's costume is determined to be red."
msgstr "我們用現代材料加固了黑色護甲。自古以來，主角的服裝就被定為紅色。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Ninja hood"
msgid_plural "Ninja hoods"
msgstr[0] "忍者頭巾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ninja hood'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "It is a set of ninja's hood, bowl and face cheeks."
msgstr "這是一套忍者的頭巾、碗狀護額和麵頰護具。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Survivor ninja hood"
msgid_plural "Survivor ninja hoods"
msgstr[0] "倖存者忍者頭巾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Survivor ninja hood'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"A reinforced ninja hood with modern materials. A compact gas mask, dual "
"structure goggles that can shield light are attached. Two characters of "
"shinobi kill are engraved on the face cheek."
msgstr "用現代材料加固的忍者頭巾。附有緊湊型防毒面具和可屏蔽光線的雙層結構護目鏡。面頰護具上刻有“忍殺”兩個字符。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Ninja chainmail"
msgid_plural "Ninja chainmails"
msgstr[0] "忍者鎖子甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ninja chainmail'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"Worn under your clothes, made of steel chain that a ninja wore for battle. "
"It is heavy and difficult to handle, but it has excellent cutting-edge "
"performance."
msgstr "穿在衣服下面，由忍者戰鬥時穿戴的鋼鏈製成。它沉重且難以操控，但具有卓越的防切割性能。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Survivor ninja chainmail"
msgid_plural "Survivor ninja chainmails"
msgstr[0] "倖存者忍者鎖子甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Survivor ninja chainmail'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"It is a lightweight body armor made of Kevlar plate and superalloy. It is "
"made to not interfere with ninja's light and light action."
msgstr "這是一種由凱夫拉板和超合金製成的輕質防彈衣。設計上不干擾忍者輕盈靈活的動作。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Ninja gloves"
msgid_plural "Ninja glovess"
msgstr[0] "忍者手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ninja gloves'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"It is a glove that a ninja wore for battle. It is reinforced with an iron "
"plate and it is sturdy. It does not disturb the movement of the fingertip."
msgstr "這是忍者戰鬥時穿戴的手套。用鐵板加固，十分堅固。不會干擾指尖的活動。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Survivor ninja gloves"
msgid_plural "Survivor ninja glovess"
msgstr[0] "倖存者忍者手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Survivor ninja gloves'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "These ninja gloves were strengthened with modern materials"
msgstr "這些忍者手套用現代材料進行了強化"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Tabi"
msgid_plural "Tabis"
msgstr[0] "足袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tabi'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"Tabi is a type of Japanese shoes with a shoe sole on socks, which is a "
"reproduction of what the ninja used."
msgstr "足袋是一種日式鞋履，在襪子上加有鞋底，這是對忍者所用之物的復刻。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Survivor ninja boots"
msgid_plural "Survivor ninja bootss"
msgstr[0] "倖存者忍者靴"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'Survivor ninja boots'}.
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "You sheath your %s"
msgstr "你將你的%s收鞘。"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'Survivor ninja boots'}.
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Sheath knife"
msgstr "收鞘刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Survivor ninja boots'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"These tabi were strengthened with modern materials. We have devised to keep "
"light movement in every environment. To that extent, the blade preventive "
"performance has been sacrificed."
msgstr "這些足袋用現代材料進行了強化。我們設計得能在各種環境中保持輕盈的移動。為此，防刃性能有所犧牲。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Starving circle"
msgid_plural "Starving circles"
msgstr[0] "飢餓之環"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Starving circle', 'str_pl': 'Starving circles'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "A ninja ration."
msgstr "一份忍者口糧。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Ninja tengu mask"
msgid_plural "Ninja tengu masks"
msgstr[0] "忍者天狗面具"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ninja tengu mask'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"Tengu is an imaginary creature in Japan and has a deep relationship with "
"mountain faith. This is a handicraft imitating the face of the Tengu, it "
"seems to be a considerable age."
msgstr "天狗是日本傳說中的虛構生物，與山嶽信仰有深厚淵源。這是一件仿照天狗面孔製作的手工藝品，看起來年代相當久遠。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Ninja jet pack"
msgid_plural "Ninja jet packs"
msgstr[0] "忍者噴氣揹包"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Ninja jet pack'}.
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "You zoom forward using your jet pack."
msgstr "你使用噴氣揹包向前疾衝。"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'Ninja jet pack'}.
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "You need rocket fuel for your jet pack."
msgstr "你的噴氣揹包需要火箭燃料。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ninja jet pack'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"It is a backpack type jet pack. Rocket fuel is necessary but high speed "
"movement is possible by flying. If the output is made too strong, it will "
"not reach the second floor of the house because it burns the buttocks."
msgstr "這是一款揹包式噴氣揹包。需要火箭燃料，但可以通過飛行實現高速移動。如果輸出功率調得過高，會因為灼傷臀部而無法抵達房屋二樓。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Ninja jet pack.(on)"
msgid_plural "Ninja jet pack.(on)s"
msgstr[0] "忍者噴氣揹包（開啟）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Ninja jet pack.(on)'}.
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "You stopped the jet pack"
msgstr "你關閉了噴氣揹包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ninja jet pack.(on)'}
#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"It is a backpack type jet pack. Rocket fuel is necessary but high speed "
"movement is possible by flying. If the output is made too strong, it will "
"not reach the second floor of the house because it burns the buttocks. It is"
" on."
msgstr ""
"這是一款揹包式噴氣揹包。需要火箭燃料，但可以通過飛行實現高速移動。如果輸出功率調得過高，會因為灼傷臀部而無法抵達房屋二樓。目前處於開啟狀態。"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid "Hand gun/AY89-3"
msgid_plural "Hand gun/AY89-3s"
msgstr[0] "手槍/AY89-3"

#: .\ninja_toos.json
msgid ""
"It is a machine pistol numbered as AY (Automatic Yakuza). Looks scary "
"corresponding to its intimidating size and weight. Design such as mounting "
"biological parts interlocking interface is strange, especially irregular "
"firing mode of 8 shots, 9 shots, 3 shots is meaning unknown and was "
"criticized. Uses Glock's 9 mm magazine."
msgstr ""
"這是一款編號為AY（自動黑幫）的衝鋒手槍。其威嚇性的尺寸和重量看起來令人畏懼。諸如搭載生物部件聯鎖接口的設計頗為怪異，尤其是8發、9發、3發的不規則射擊模式意義不明，曾受到批評。使用格洛克9毫米彈匣。"

